desc: Welcome to EMBARK Collection! As we venture out on a new journey in life, there will always be a working dog doing the same. 10% of every EMBARK purchase supports Dogs on Duty. Helping the working dogs who help us. Start your journey supporting another!

layout.text: Whether just beginning or you’ve been on your journey for some time... on land, in water, or air... EMBARK will provide you with the casual-wear you need for any adventure.
